snippet.textDisplay: I’ve seen it, Australia midnight screening, if you’ve watched spoiler videos or heard the leaks then you have the story laid out already. It’s very fast paced, most of the humour fell flat with the audience I was with, the plot is ridiculous with throw away lines as there’s no time given for exposition. Certainly a tonne of fan service and ridiculous force powers (ugh) even though I wasn’t a fan of the Rose character, she is totally under used in this movie and it’s clear as day there were appropriate times she could have been used. JJ was bold? No way would I call this bold. I would call it fan fiction. Save your money or go see Jumanji 2.
